er to control, as it would allow for scrolling and multitouch, which would improve this device’s usability.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/58033-garmin-nuvi-2797lmt13.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/YjpJaMsLUHyRfVBv5XvsWd.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"YjpJaMsLUHyRfVBv5XvsWd","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/YjpJaMsLUHyRfVBv5XvsWd.jpg","alt":""},"id":"1d70027d-50c4-4770-97e9-27d0b52a0e21","type":"image"},{"data":{"text":"Destination"},"id":"91cd3777-3105-40ea-ba74-9e47da2787cc","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/WiSxgaSEm6jesxUULcyhrS.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"You will find Garmin Real Directions pre-installed on your Nuvi 2797LMT. This feature makes it easier understand the directions you are given. When making a turn, the device is programmed to use buildings, stoplights and other landmarks specific to that location, making it easier for you to know when to turn. Your Nuvi 2797LMT can do this due in part to map updates. To keep your maps current, the Nuvi 2797LMT comes with four free map updates a year for the lifetime of your device. Should you choose to, you can purchase additional maps for other areas on the Nuvi website. By keeping your maps updated, you allow the device to better identify landmarks and help you find your destination.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/58033-garmin-nuvi-2797lmt17.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/WiSxgaSEm6jesxUULcyhrS.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"WiSxgaSEm6jesxUULcyhrS","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/WiSxgaSEm6jesxUULcyhrS.jpg","alt":""},"id":"6da8da0c-a065-4226-8285-61e60f9c431c","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["This device also comes with lifetime traffic updates. This GPS unit can save you time by re-routing you before you reach a traffic jam. If an accident has been reported, you will receive the update as soon as it is available. This will save you valuable time, as it will provide you the opportunity to take a different route. If the traffic is unavoidable, then the Nuvi 2797LMT can give you an accurate estimation of the delay.","The lithium-ion battery installed in the Nuvi 2797LMT can&#39;t be removed, but it is rechargeable. You charge the battery by keeping it plugged into your vehicle while it is running. However, this GPS device only has an hour of battery life if you choose to use it while it is unplugged from the power source. You can connect your smartphone to the navigation system using Bluetooth or the free Garmin app. Bluetooth will allow you to make and answer calls using the device, and the Garmin app will let you share destinations and waypoints with your phone, along with telling you where you parked."]},"id":"39ca61af-ac88-47fb-b810-7858dfd855ff","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Design"},"id":"b7aad127-9939-47c9-a990-cb544c2b9e5d","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/nQk6wSGzmZf7weuEGj4Y8m.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"Your device will come preloaded with 10 million points of interest (POIs). These are preprogrammed locations such as businesses, banks, gas stations, landmarks, restaurants and more. If you can&#39;t find what you are looking for, you can create your own custom POIs. Along with the POIs, you can create up to 1,000 waypoints. These waypoints are places that you want to mark specifically for future reference, such as your favorite restaurant or the location of your kids&#39; dance studio. You can save up to 100  custom routes, whether it is to the dog groomer or a combination of several POIs and waypoints. If you use multiple destination when creating a route, the Nuvi 2797LMT will sort those locations and create the most efficient route for you to follow.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/58033-garmin-nuvi-2797lmt11.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nQk6wSGzmZf7weuEGj4Y8m.jpg","credit":"","a